title: ETA on Project figures from awhile ago?
body:
https://na.merch.riotgames.com/en/collectibles/figures/project-fiora-action-figure.html

I ordered one of those awhile ago and was just wondering when I could expect it?

I know it says preorder so I'm wondering how long it will take before its completed and then sent?

replies.body:
I looked into this and it looks like we are aiming to have them ship out towards the end of the year. I can't provide an exact ETA on this, but I hope this helped.

Let me know if you have any questions.
That answered my question. Thanks for the response :D
